> When I started reading this group several months ago, I thought I'd learn
> a  little about cryptology. Well that's exactly what I've learned, very
> little.  I have however learned quite a bit about David Sternlight and
> those who fuel  the wild tangents that this group has spun to, more often
> than not. I have  seen numerous requests to split the group, let's do it!
> There's been talk of  a moderated group. I don't like this as much, but if
> that's what it takes, let's do it. Let's do whatever we need to do to
> limit the topic to the  Science of Cryptography (or about PGP for those in
